org.cloudbus.cloudsim
Class CloudletSchedulerTimeShared

java.lang.Object
  org.cloudbus.cloudsim.CloudletScheduler
      org.cloudbus.cloudsim.CloudletSchedulerTimeShared
Direct Known Subclasses:
CloudletSchedulerDynamicWorkload
public class CloudletSchedulerTimeShared
extends CloudletScheduler

CloudletSchedulerTimeShared implements a policy of scheduling performed by a virtual machine. Cloudlets execute time-shared in VM.

Since:
CloudSim Toolkit 1.0
